        id: "rsa-ed25519",
        fn: "Ed25519 / RSA — public-key signing and verification",
        desc: "Sign a payload with a private key; anyone with the public key can verify. Ed25519 is the default for new code (smaller, faster, fewer parameter footguns); RSA persists for legacy compatibility (JWT RS256, X.509 certs, S/MIME).",
        category: "Asymmetric Crypto",
